{"tid":196017,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"恰恰VS啱啱?［正字撚請入］","createTime":"2017-04-11T04:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T16:03:14.000Z","uid":88812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d88f3ace8e939516c1414ffaeb28c38740a72a8","tid":196017,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟好多年前試過用廣東話寫小說。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">屌你，我手寫我口，竟然唔係用作為好多年前官方語言廣東話。</span><br />\n咁有啲字我都唔識寫返出來，於是我上網查下。<br />\n其中一個係「恰恰」，我成日見到人寫做「啱啱」<br />\n<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">寫岩岩嗰啲收皮</span></del><br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=259994e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/</a><br />\n當時我查到恰字既異讀音就係「啱」<br />\n而佢解釋就係恰好、恰巧、恰到好處、 恰似、 恰如其分<br />\n咁真係恰恰好啦！<br />\n啱唔啱啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84071ecf3fe90dd5c4fc10388daa5834c3099459","tid":196017,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"岩！"},{"pid":"dd8e1b269b1aa3c5de9cc8e8aea87ed24c757daa","tid":196017,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩！</blockquote><br />\n岩啊<br />\n我寫恰恰真係冇人明我噏乜囉"},{"pid":"3ebdef062449e8cb57d812ac4632d3cc0def5d86","tid":196017,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T05:25:53.000Z","msg":"有啲正字已經約定俗成寫做第個寫法<br />\n如果下下追尋返正字（即係乸閪、hum bang lang嗰啲嘅正寫）又會令人睇唔明<br />\n不妨跟坊間通用嘅新寫法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過恰恰真係未聽過"},{"pid":"8b0bdd5892ebf018b10a88c03a03f50e8480ea89","tid":196017,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲正字已經約定俗成寫做第個寫法<br />\n如果